Dragonscribe
An unofficial save editor for RuneScape: Dragonwilds.

RuneScape and RuneScape: Dragonwilds are trademarks of Jagex Limited. This
project is unofficial and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Jagex Limited.

The save-format research that makes this tool possible was pioneered by the
community. In particular, the world-mode and char_type mechanics were first
documented by haithemobeidi in the RSDragonWilds-WorldEditor project
(https://github.com/haithemobeidi/RSDragonWilds-WorldEditor). Dragonscribe is
an independent, clean-room reimplementation; no source code was copied. Credit
and thanks for the reverse-engineering groundwork.

This application uses the following third-party packages, each distributed
under its own license:

- pywebview
- psutil

The standalone build is produced with PyInstaller.
